<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans Stieber</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Herausgabe des von Hildebrand Holzschuhmacher gekauften Holzes.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_104" id="51v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_104_r2l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hanſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l2">Stieber /</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_104_r2l3">Lieber her Hans / vns hat fürgelegt / . Hiltprant Holcʒſchumacher </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l4">vnſer Burger vvie er etwieuil holcʒes vmb ew kaufft hab . / daʒ er nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l5">gerne arbeiten wolt . / daran Jr Jn hindert . / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l6">willen . / dem <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Burger volgen / vnd Jn daran vngehindert </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_104_r2l7">laſʒen wöllet . / Als vvir ew etc daʒ wollen etc - / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Georij . x<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_104" id="51v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen Stieber</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Hans, uns hat fürgelegt Hiltprant Holczschumacher, unser burger,
                        wie er etwievil holczes umb ew kaufft hab, daz er nu gerne arbeiten wolt,
                        daran ir in hindert. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger volgen und in daran ungehindert laszen
                        wöllet, als wir ew etc. Daz wollen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Georii x<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
